after them

*Obećaj* da ćeš doći na večeru (Promise that you'll come to dinner).

*Obećao* sam da ću doći na večeru (I promised that I will come to dinner).

*Obećanja* su se poštovala (The promises were kept).

*Obećanje* je bilo da će svi doći (The promise was that everyone will come).

*Obećavam* da ću biti na vreme (I promise to be on time).